00:40:06,059 --> 00:40:08,392
I heard there was a great
startup company around here

769
00:40:13,326 --> 00:40:17,125
Victoria called me today
to fire me.

770
00:40:17,192 --> 00:40:20,559
I guess she didn't know
you already did that.

771
00:40:20,626 --> 00:40:22,192
So, what do you say?

772
00:40:22,259 --> 00:40:23,725
You looking?

773
00:40:23,792 --> 00:40:25,858
I might be.

774
00:40:25,925 --> 00:40:28,925
It'll be long hours,
horrible pay,

775
00:40:28,992 --> 00:40:31,892
And no job security.

776
00:40:31,959 --> 00:40:33,025
[ Laughs ]

777
00:40:33,092 --> 00:40:35,159
It sounds perfect.

778
00:40:35,226 --> 00:40:36,593
[ Laughs ]

779
00:40:46,292 --> 00:40:50,059
[ Laughing evilly ]

780
00:40:50,125 --> 00:40:52,659
[ Gasps ]

781
00:40:57,492 --> 00:40:59,593
You think
you can kill me?

782
00:40:59,659 --> 00:41:02,659
You can't kill me.
I'm still here.

783
00:41:02,725 --> 00:41:04,725
[ Laughs evilly ]

784
00:41:04,792 --> 00:41:07,426
I already called the police.
They're on their way.

785
00:41:07,492 --> 00:41:09,593
So? What are they
gonna do?

786
00:41:09,659 --> 00:41:12,059
I'll get out,
and i'll come back.

787
00:41:12,125 --> 00:41:13,626
[ Laughs evilly ]

788
00:41:13,693 --> 00:41:15,659
Do you remember
what i told you i'd do

789
00:41:15,725 --> 00:41:18,092
If you ever
came near my family again?

790
00:41:18,159 --> 00:41:19,693
I told you i'd kill you.

791
00:41:19,758 --> 00:41:21,693
But you didn't.

792
00:41:21,758 --> 00:41:24,492
I'm not dead.

793
00:41:24,559 --> 00:41:26,858
Sure you are.

